name: Coin Crush
description: This is a fun game on HEN. First you have to click on "Start Game" button at the bottom of the page. Then set similar crypto coins on triple or quad series horizontally or vertically by mouse drag and drop. Each triple series has 1 point and each quad series has 2 points. You just have 120 seconds time to gain maximum point. After that there will be appeared an QRCode, so by scanning that, your score and name will be recorded on main server and then the scoreboard will be appeared. Top three points of the each week will be announced as winners and will receive awesome NFTs by their choice of giveaway pack. The scoreboard is common to all games listed on my page. For more and future details visit https://games.safoura.art and discord.gg/v3HGdGuT
